Travis Avenue, north side, about 50 feet east of South Avenue. James Butler's map of 1853 and Beers's map of 1874 show the house to have been owned bv W.F. Carey. From 1898 on it belonged to Villiam T. Meredith.

November 1, 1922
By W1lliam T. Davis through P.L. Sperr
